  "notes": [
    "This study used an in vitro triple-culture model with Caco-2, HT29-MTX-E12, and THP-1 cells to investigate ST3Gal1's role in intestinal barrier function",
    "ST3Gal1 knockdown improved barrier function while overexpression impaired it, particularly under inflammatory conditions",
    "The study provides evidence for ST3Gal1 as a potential therapeutic target for ulcerative colitis"
  ]
